author: KEXP
description:
http://KEXP.ORG presents Den Der Hale performing live at the l’Antipode in Rennes, France, during Trans Musicales 2024. Recorded December 05, 2024. 

Songs:
The Horse From Turin 00:00
By Pastoral Light 06:01
To Begin 10:07
The Frail 20:28

Pontus Lindskogen - Guitar, Vocals, Mixer with Tape Loops
Mimosa Baker - Synth, Drum Pad, Vocals
Max Bredberg - Guitar
Ejner Pedersen Trenter - Bass Guitar
Axel Nelson - Drums, Background Vocals

Audio & Mastering Engineer/ Audio Mixer: : Matt Ogaz

Cameras: Jim Beckmann, Carlos Cruz, Scott Holpainen & Luke Knecht
Editor: Jim Beckmann
